title: Murder on the High Seas/Love Bound (1932) PRE-CODE HOLLYWOOD

sources.title: Murder on the High Seas/Love Bound (1932) PRE-CODE HOLLYWOOD
sources.description:
Stars: Jack Mulhall, Natalie Moorhead, Clara Kimball Young 
Director: Robert F. Hill

A beautiful woman is awarded a fortune in a breach-of-promise lawsuit, destroying the reputation of a wealthy broker. Posing as a millionaire, his son sets sail for Europe aboard a luxury liner on a mission to expose the wicked woman and her criminal accomplices.

This film was initially released in theaters as LOVE BOUND in 1932. It was packaged for TV broadcast in 1949 and re-titled MURDER ON THE HIGH SEAS.
